{"tid":656643,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：我會坐北看台柴新領隊台！","createTime":"2018-05-07T11:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T17:23:13.000Z","uid":4661,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0a616b25be034d50a2f59ea41ae708a5394c2a7d","tid":656643,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"好小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i2-prod.irishmirror.ie/incoming/article10126105.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/MAIN-Arsenal-v-Lincoln-City-The-Emirates-FA-Cup-Sixth-Round-Football-The-Emirates-London-UK-11-Mar.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.irishmirror.ie%2Fincoming%2Farticle10126105.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2FMAIN-Arsenal-v-Lincoln-City-The-Emirates-FA-Cup-Sixth-Round-Football-The-Emirates-London-UK-11-Mar.jpg&h=96408106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Bi0bwX9JPWi7%2FEyeJDEgz5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f5e3e8c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴領隊雲加於周日大勝般尼5:0後，除了發表告別感言外，還在記者會開玩笑說，「我會回來鬧新領隊。」<br />\n<br />\n帶領阿仙奴長達22年的雲加（Arsene Wenger）說到對未來的展望，「這對我來說是一個新的開始。我必須學會如何重新與自己聯繫，並組織我生活中的一切。 22年來，我不得不忘記自己的感受，去關心我需要解決的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n最後一次在酋長球場開賽後記者會的雲加，被問到日後會否回酋長球場觀看比賽時，他開玩笑說，「現在我有更多自己的時間了，我很樂意有一天去到北看台，然後我可以對下一任領隊大喊大叫！」<br />\n<br />\n「不過還要取決於我是否到其他地方工作，我的下一份工作是否會有時間讓我這樣做。」法國人續說。"},{"pid":"9fd84c5d67516225147e348a875be15d1e7f7833","tid":656643,"uid":55,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f342111a61c645c30617de14130440c74cede27","tid":656643,"uid":15886,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"雲加睇得好通透  佢知道佢一走咗 阿記就肯定玩完"},{"pid":"4ca3a8a471f4a915db1b18a069e00d662c55b050","tid":656643,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"自從